Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:34.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay, mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:39.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:41.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I won't. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:51.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Where did you go, my baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Papa, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:19.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:24.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was just by mama's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:27.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It seemed like she was having a hard time sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:31.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:47.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Because of that, you're always needlessly holding yourself back, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're getting the wrong impression, papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:55.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I haven't thought of it like that even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What happened on that day was a shock for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:06.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't been affected emotionally by the event, mama and I may never have noticed the screams coming from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:13.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It must have been an incredibly heavy load for a sixteen year old to carry alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,As parents, that's something we must bear the responsibility for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:24.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's why I agree with grandfather's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:33.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You should paint your life on a pure white canvas freely without having to worry about who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:37.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You can't just give and take in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll just take what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can give in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:53.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Mama, grandfather, and I have already received plenty from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:10.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I apologize for my absence until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Too bad about the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:22.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,President, I've come today to pick up the form for quitting the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Does this have anything to do with your loss in the election?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I have personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought this day might come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I retire from the club because of exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,you might be ostracized by other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:51.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I want you to serve as the face of the Drama club from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Stay in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The other members can learn a lot of things from you when it comes to acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:05.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you can't get along with the older members, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Become my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:15.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you become the club president's sister, you won't be attacked anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even next year, becoming my sister won't lose its effect that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Fukuzawa Yumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You like her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've been looking at you this entire time, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:40.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be fine if you can be happy by becoming Yumi-san's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:45.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But you've come back here, hurt, while trying to get closer to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There must be something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:53.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you don't change, you won't be able to walk with Yumi-san together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:06:00.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So in order for you to distance yourself from the Yamayuri Council and the Rose Mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:03.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,you ran in an election you knew you would lose, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It hurts to see you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:17.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Forget about Yumi-san already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:34.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I cannot choose the club president in order to separate myself from Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm lying in an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So I don't stand out, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to ask about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's about what happened at Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:58.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why did you say something like that to Yumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:03.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't understand your feelings, even though I know you like Yumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Who did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I can tell just by looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're not very persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:16.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you go to Canada last summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When you heard that Yumi-chan was going to the Ogasawara's villa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,you changed your plans, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:31.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,At the time, I thought you decided to go to the villa in order to interfere with the two of them because you were jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko, you were worried about Yumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What're you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:40.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You knew those girls were dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So what if I did go to the villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:49.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even then, you didn't go to a foreign country that would take you far away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:08:00.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You were afraid that the bullying you received would happen to Yumi-chan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Exactly who did it and when did they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Was it Kyougoku? Ayanokouji? Saionji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I never noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:23.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Up until the moment you ran away from home, I had believed that you didn't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I have to pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You saved me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't made me stop, it would've been dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You saved me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Since we made it on time to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:56.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama, I wasn't that shocked by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've already detached myself from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:04.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to become that angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you become happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're running away from the happiness in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:16.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You adore Yumi-chan. {I decided adore worked better than words like yearn or attached to.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:31.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me that I should have accepted her rosary that time, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-chan chose you as her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you so surprised after all that's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything specific about what's happened between you and Yumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's why I tricked you into telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't tell such an obvious lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why do you doubt me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:54.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to trust and then be betrayed, I'd rather not trust in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:55.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:59.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Although you say you don't trust others, deep down inside you do want to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,While you run away, you wait for someone to chase after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's not-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:09.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you keep running away like that, no one's going to chase after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:16.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone attacking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:18.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It must be because everyone likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:23.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Attacked because I'm liked? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The world's filled with things that can't be understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So you waited in ambush to ask me that?{edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why did you go this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,About what happened between you and Yumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you think about it, you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:21.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Treasure hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, over there! {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:25.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Exactly one year ago, during last year's treasure hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I saw her for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:39.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This was the person that Sachiko onee-sama had chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought she was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It was just a vague feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:47.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,...of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Well then, good day everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good day to you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You seem busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you heading towards the Rosa Mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nope, today I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry because they're doing a special on Buddha statues on T.V.!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Anyway, good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:32.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:35.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:42.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It must be tough! You're hiding your card this year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The three second years are hiding their treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I remember, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:58.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've already read it, and I can see it at the Rosa Mansion at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The three second years are hiding their treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:33.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,G-Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then let's walk together until the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did you need me for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:56.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's like first calling out to a friend to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:59.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then wondering why I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes... {ie}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:15.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Before thinking about it, I offered you my rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:19.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Without actually thinking about your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I got ahead of myself thinking about my own feelings.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I think it's obvious that you'd be shocked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That was my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And now this is a suggestion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:33.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,can we return our relationship to how it was before Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:38.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what's inside your heart, Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:42.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so tolerant to an underclassman that refused your rosary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:47.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why did you think of making someone like me your sister in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Can you stop saying self-depreciating things like "people like me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For people like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"People like me" fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've already decided that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,what you did was due to your own confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've accepted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even then, why do you still bother with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking ever since I was refused by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:23.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"How will things go between us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:28.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I should have thought about what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After that, I understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:36.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly fine if you can be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:41.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Me being myself," you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:48.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So no matter what you do, I won't falter with my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even when it came to your reason for running in the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:55.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I didn't dig for it when you didn't tell me your reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:16:00.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's also the same when you ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What kind of people your parents are,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,what your relationship with them is like now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,or what kind of childhood you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:16.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Those things are of an entirely different dimension than the feeling of embracing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that how it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:30.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What happened that time was, in the end, just your pity for me, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:34.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You just wanted to be charitable on the Holy Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:39.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When you handed that rosary to me, it must've felt good, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I can be myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could wish for me to be your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But now I've finally solved the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:57.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you did it unconsciously, then it's even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Aren't you misunderstanding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:16:59.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't come toward me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:02.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't get any closer to me than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:03.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear any excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:17.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say now, it seems like you won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:23.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:27.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Count to one hundred from where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't move before you've finished counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:47.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten, eleven, twelve,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:52.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,thirteen, fourteen, fifteen, sixteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:57.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Forty-seven, forty-eight, forty-nine, fifty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:06.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ninety-five, ninety-six, ninety-seven, ninety-eight, ninety-nine, one hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:19.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did you say anything to Yumi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:24.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Tell me clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:31.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It seems like you've come to me to complain about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but if you don't say it clearly, I won't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's about my birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Your birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You remember it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So? When did you tell her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:46.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Like I said, what're you-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:52.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the fact that I'm not the Matsudairas' daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:19:01.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan, you aren't the daughter Mr. Matsudaira and Mrs. Matsudaira gave birth to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, this is my first time hearing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then someone must've told her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:18.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Suguru onii-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't look like he had said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:27.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really, you've been patronizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:31.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Not to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:37.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Yumi has no idea about your family circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:44.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even if she found out on accident, she's not the type of girl who would change how she sees you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:49.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I know this the best because I'm her older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:02.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Although, I've started to pity Yumi, who only thinks about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then everything was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:30.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I should do anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Count to one hundred from where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:44.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six, seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:47.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm now alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:48.76,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,...eight, nine... {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I cut my bonds that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.53,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,...ten, eleven... {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I had been connected to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:54.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,...twelve, thirteen... {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:54.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:59.53,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Thirty-one, thirty-two, thirty-three... {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:06.35,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,...thirty-four, thirty-five, thirty-six... {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It didn't matter who. I wanted them by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:11.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you keep running away like that, no one's going to chase after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:14.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Fifty-six, fifty-seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:16.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of counting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:20.04,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,...fifty-eight, fifty-nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:23.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of opening my eyes, and finding myself all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:36.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Seventy-five, seventy-six, seventy-seven, seventy-eight, seventy-nine, eighty, eighty-one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I was thinking I probably shouldn't interrupt, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:46.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Didn't you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:50.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After leaving, I felt a bit worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But the special...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:56.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:03.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:05.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:08.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:10.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What happened exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:15.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Maria-sama, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.07,0:22:18.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you for returning Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:24.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:28.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,-ED-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:07.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Today's Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.26,0:24:11.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I ended up receiving chocolate from Mami-san and her sister from the newspaper club!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:12.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wha- Chocolate from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:15.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Mami-san, you should say "Thank you" first, shouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:16.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That "first" is unnecessary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:18.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And after that, "I'm very happy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.78,0:24:20.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I-I'm very happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.38,0:24:22.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I'm the demon of Lilian's newspaper club!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.55,0:24:25.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just because it's Valentine's Day doesn't mean all you do is be joyful!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:27.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Next time: Crisscross.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.73,0:24:30.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How'll this year's treasure hunt go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.14,0:24:32.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Who'll be searching for our cards?
