Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:14.91,roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}{\pos(158,10)}Shiroi kizu ookiku hiroge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:14.91,english,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Open up your pale wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:22.01,hira,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}宝箱隠しにいこう
